1
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:32,280
You don't go for your Hundred Treasures Order.

2
00:00:32,719 --> 00:00:33,600
Why are you here?

3
00:00:34,539 --> 00:00:35,039
Qian,

4
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:37,640
you really have a lot of leisure.

5
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:38,780
Why has you changed

6
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:40,179
so much recently?

7
00:00:40,479 --> 00:00:42,420
And this talisman

8
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,399
was given by my wife.

9
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:49,840
Qian,

10
00:00:50,579 --> 00:00:52,320
if you meet someone in the future

11
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:53,939
like the moon and the lamp,

12
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:55,579
you will know why I am

13
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:56,719
why I'm willing to do this.

14
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:04,579
Xie Lingfeng,

15
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,180
let me go.

16
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,420
Military power, wealth, and the Hundred Treasures Order,

17
00:01:12,420 --> 00:01:13,260
I can give up everything

18
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,319
and give you everything.

19
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:17,400
I just want my wife.

20
00:01:21,340 --> 00:01:22,700
You wishful thinking.

21
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:35,060
My brother is crazy.

22
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,500
I'm not sane either.

23
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,280
I know she hates me and betrays me,

24
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,620
[but still want to see her.]

25
00:01:40,459 --> 00:01:41,260
[Even if it's just]

26
00:01:41,939 --> 00:01:43,260
[to hear her voice.]

27
00:01:51,099 --> 00:01:51,620
Luo Yao.

28
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:53,980
Is that you?

29
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,000
Who's there?

30
00:02:05,219 --> 00:02:05,920
[Su Luoyao.]

31
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,259
[Is your heart made of iron?]

32
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,080
[If you want revenge,]

33
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,599
[I'm willing to hold the blade for you.]

34
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,680
[But since you've made me your slave,]

35
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,740
why do you abandon me like a worn-out shoe?

36
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,439
I don't want to see anyone today.

37
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,099
Luo Yao,

38
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,159
I beg you to let me see him.

39
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,280
Even if it's just a glance.

40
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:22,139
Stop.

41
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:25,979
If you come any closer,

42
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:28,819
we

43
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,219
will never see each other again.

44
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,919
Then I'll just wait here

45
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:52,139
until you're willing to see me.

46
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:02,919
[Even if I go to hell,]

47
00:04:03,939 --> 00:04:05,520
[I will never let you go.]

48
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:08,819
[Don't even think about leaving me.]

49
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,779
Will you come with me?

50
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:04,860
Xie Huaiyun.

51
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:05,899
Let her go.

52
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:22,100
Do you really want to go?

53
00:05:23,939 --> 00:05:24,839
If we stay in the Hundred Treasures Office,

54
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,560
our father won't let us go.

55
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:28,120
Why don't I

56
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,740
take you to travel around the world?

57
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:31,839
[and leave this deceitful world behind.]

58
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,199
[You and I,]

59
00:05:34,379 --> 00:05:35,139
[spending the rest of our lives together.]

60
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,060
I came in a hurry,

61
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:40,240
only remember the left mountain road

62
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:41,100
has a beautiful scenery.

63
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,459
Since we're leaving,

64
00:05:42,939 --> 00:05:44,480
why don't you accompany me to see it again?

65
00:05:59,019 --> 00:05:59,759
We've been traveling all night,

66
00:06:00,139 --> 00:06:00,899
my lady, you must be tired.

67
00:06:02,459 --> 00:06:03,519
But the Xie Family Army

68
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,240
is likely on our trail.

69
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:06,540
We should...
My lord,

70
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,100
do you

71
00:06:11,540 --> 00:06:12,839
recognize this place?

72
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,600
What?

73
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,000
My lady,

74
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:23,600
are you alright?

75
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:26,939
I mean,

76
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:29,639
my lord,

77
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,879
do you remember this place?

78
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,060
This is

79
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:47,100
the temple from eight years ago.

80
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,800
Do you remember

81
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,560
Su Heng,

82
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:02,439
whom you killed with your own hands?

83
00:07:10,699 --> 00:07:11,720
My brother joined

84
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,800
the Xie Family Army at 15,

85
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:14,800
building a name for himself.

86
00:07:15,699 --> 00:07:16,300
In the end,

87
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:17,339
he died

88
00:07:17,339 --> 00:07:19,480
at the hands of your own people.

89
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:21,100
Not just him,

90
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:24,180
but also the 300 soldiers behind him.

91
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,139
I even

92
00:07:30,779 --> 00:07:33,240
buried their bodies myself.

93
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,560
Xie Huaiyun,

94
00:07:42,899 --> 00:07:43,699
now,

95
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:48,899
do you know who I am?

96
00:07:49,459 --> 00:07:50,000
You are

97
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,720
Su Heng's sister.

98
00:07:58,420 --> 00:07:58,920
I...

99
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,600
I'm sorry.

100
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,279
I'm so sorry.

101
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,319
Sorry?

102
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,180
When you

103
00:08:08,339 --> 00:08:09,740
stabbed him in the chest,

104
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:11,740
did you ever think about being sorry?

105
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:22,939
What exactly

106
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:24,319
happened eight years ago?

107
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,439
What crime did those
300 soldiers commit

108
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,240
that they were slaughtered

109
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,259
in one night?

110
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:31,759
What secret

111
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,519
does that painting hold?

112
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:35,620
Tell me!

113
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:39,940
So,

114
00:08:40,460 --> 00:08:42,000
it's all about that painting.

115
00:08:44,059 --> 00:08:46,019
If this is your true purpose,

116
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,740
does that mean your redemption of me

117
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:50,960
was all a lie?

118
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,500
Don't you

119
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:56,019
have any

120
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,000
feelings for me?

121
00:08:58,879 --> 00:08:59,360
An Rao,

122
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:00,460
I don't believe it.

123
00:09:01,179 --> 00:09:01,980
I don't believe it.

124
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:10,399
That night,

125
00:09:11,659 --> 00:09:13,480
you painted a lotus on my chest.

126
00:09:15,059 --> 00:09:16,539
You said the lotus is pure

127
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,820
and you hope I can be free from suffering.

128
00:09:20,419 --> 00:09:22,860
Was all of this a lie?

129
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:28,779
Please tell me.

130
00:09:30,179 --> 00:09:30,899
Tell me.

131
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:41,519
Xie Huaiyun,

132
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,639
are you stupid

133
00:09:45,899 --> 00:09:47,620
or naive?

134
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,799
There are only evil spirits

135
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,360
that come out of hell,

136
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:58,879
not any goddess.

137
00:10:29,019 --> 00:10:30,299
Xie Huaiyun,

138
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:33,379
the redemption you long for,

139
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,639
and the An Rao you love,

140
00:10:38,179 --> 00:10:40,019
never existed.

141
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,960
In this world,

142
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,419
no one has ever treated you sincerely.

143
00:10:49,379 --> 00:10:50,679
The blood debts

144
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:54,679
you owe

145
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,179
are irredeemable.
